Title: 13.1.2 Integer Types (Exact Value) - INTEGER, INT, SMALLINT, TINYINT, MEDIUMINT, BIGINT
Description: A small integer. The signed range is -32768 to 32767. The unsigned range is 0 to 65535.
Type: SMALLINT; Storage (Bytes): 2; Minimum Value Signed: -32768; Maximum Value Signed: 32767; Minimum Value Unsigned: 0; Maximum Value Unsigned: 65535
